ht","name":"Heading","type":"text","html":"<h5 style=\"text-align:center;\">Called to Serve</h5>","description":"Plain Text","draggable":true,"content":"Called to Serve","position":0,"fullName":"content:text:4:68","htmlElement":"h5","styles":{"textAlign":"center"},"primarytype":"content","newLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","oldLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","id":"content:text:4:68","contentOverride":false,"manualContent":"Called to Serve"},"content:textarea:5:49":{"icon":"align-justify","name":"Paragraph","type":"textarea","html":"<p>Serving on a Salvation Army&nbsp;Advisory Board or Council presents an extraordinary opportunity to make a profound and lasting impact on both the organization and your own community.</p>","description":"Mixed Plain and Rich Text","draggable":true,"content":"Serving on a Salvation Army&nbsp;Advisory Board or Council presents an extraordinary opportunity to make a profound and lasting impact on both the organization and your own community.","position":1,"fullName":"content:textarea:5:49","htmlElement":"p","styles":{},"primarytype":"content","newLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","oldLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","id":"content:textarea:5:49","contentOverride":false,"manualContent":"Serving on a Salvation Army&nbsp;Advisory Board or Council presents an extraordinary opportunity to make a profound and lasting impact on both the organization and your own community."},"content:textarea:6:36":{"icon":"align-justify","name":"Paragraph","type":"textarea","html":"<p>As a member, you become a champion of The Salvation Army's mission, advocating for positive change and harnessing your unique skills and expertise to drive meaningful progress. By lending your voice and strategic insights, you have the power to shape the direction, policies, and initiatives of our organization. This opportunity allows you to collaborate with like-minded individuals, building a network of passionate and influential changemakers who share your commitment to creating a better world. Moreover, serving on a non-profit advisory board offers personal and professional growth opportunities, enabling you to broaden your horizons, strengthen your leadership abilities, and deepen your understanding of social and economic challenges. It is a chance to leave a lasting legacy and be part of a collective force for good, leaving an indelible mark on the lives of those we serve and inspiring others to join the cause.</p>","description":"Mixed Plain and Rich Text","draggable":true,"content":"As a member, you become a champion of The Salvation Army's mission, advocating for positive change and harnessing your unique skills and expertise to drive meaningful progress. By lending your voice and strategic insights, you have the power to shape the direction, policies, and initiatives of our organization. This opportunity allows you to collaborate with like-minded individuals, building a network of passionate and influential changemakers who share your commitment to creating a better world. Moreover, serving on a non-profit advisory board offers personal and professional growth opportunities, enabling you to broaden your horizons, strengthen your leadership abilities, and deepen your understanding of social and economic challenges. It is a chance to leave a lasting legacy and be part of a collective force for good, leaving an indelible mark on the lives of those we serve and inspiring others to join the cause.","position":2,"fullName":"content:textarea:6:36","htmlElement":"p","styles":{},"primarytype":"content","newLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","oldLoc":"design:columns:2columnswideright:7:67-4:2 Columns - Left Small:1","id":"content:textarea:6:36","contentOverride":false,"manualContent":"As a member, you become a champion of The Salvation Army's mission, advocating for positive change and harnessing your unique skills and expertise to drive meaningful progress. By lending your voice and strategic insights, you have the power to shape the direction, policies, and initiatives of our organization. This opportunity allows you to collaborate with like-minded individuals, building a network of passionate and influential changemakers who share your commitment to creating a better world. Moreover, serving on a non-profit advisory board offers personal and professional growth opportunities, enabling you to broaden your horizons, strengthen your leadership abilities, and deepen your understanding of social and economic challenges. It is a chance to leave a lasting legacy and be part of a collective force for good, leaving an indelible mark on the lives of those we serve and inspiring others to join the cause."}}}}},"design:design:whitespace-sm:8:59":{"uid":"351","name":"Whitespace - Small","type":"design","html":"<div class=\"my-2\"></div>","preview":"<div style=\"border-style:dashed; height:10px; width:100%;\"></div>","classes":"my-2","droppable":true,"position":1,"fullName":"design:design:whitespace-sm:8:59","primarytype":"design","newLoc":"design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:72:60-1:1 column - 1 row:0","oldLoc":"design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:72:60-1:1 column - 1 row:0"},"content:wysiwyg_basic:9:75":{"icon":"outdent","name":"WYSIWYG","type":"wysiwyg_basic","html":"<div class=\"text-white rounded p-6 gap-3 my-5\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:300px;background-image:url(\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/ba1ae43a-1116-430b-a313-47c06d536cc0_Blue+BG.png'); background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover;\">\n<div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 2;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"position: relative; z-index: 3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; min-height: 300px;\">\n<div style=\"width: 100%; pad